############################################################
#
#  ILDConfig - package for ilcsoft configuration files
#  such as Marlin steering files, gear geometry files,...
#  related to ILD (or CLIC_ILD)
#
#  01/2012
#  F.Gaede, DESY
############################################################

This new package just combines the old packages StandardConfig and MokkaDBConfig,
which will be obsolete form now on (iLCSoft release v01-13-03).



subdirectories:

 StandardConfig/
 ----------------
    current
    -------
    current example files for running Mokka and Marlin
    (see: ./current/README for mini howto on using (this version of) ilcsoft )
     
    
    mc2008
    ------
    configuration files for 2008 Monte Carlo production for LOI
    
    
    clic_cdr
    ------
    configuration files for CLIC CDR production (2011)


 MokkaDBConfig/
 -------------

    current dump of the Mokka DB: mokka-dbdump.sql.tgz

    
    scripts
    -------
    scripts for related to running Mokka or the Mokka DB 




 versions:
 ========

 --------
| v00-01 |
 --------
    first version based on 

        - StandardConfig  v03-51-01
	  with fixes: 
          -  bbudsc_stdreco.xml: removed picking up of Si-hits in Clupatra 
             and fixed collections and types for DST  

        - MokkaDBConfig v03-06

